Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么开始点名了
