Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,内田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在
